---
title: "Get Started"
---

### Get ready to build
Follow these steps to set up your environment and start making requests.

<Steps>
  <Step title="Process Overview">
    Sign up for the [CoinBridge Dashboard](https://dashboard.coinbridge.com) to access your developer portal and sandbox environment.
  </Step>
</Steps>

---

### Explore by use case
CoinBridge provides the infrastructure for various financial flows. Select a path below to see specific implementation guides.

<CardGroup cols={2}>
  <Card title="Virtual Card Issuance" icon="credit-card" href="/docs/android-sdk/account-setup/create-virtual-card">
    Generate instant virtual cards for your users with customizable spending limits.
  </Card>
  <Card title="Mobile Contactless Payments" icon="nfc" href="/docs/android-sdk/payment/index">
    Enable Tap-to-Pay and digital wallet integrations for a seamless checkout.
  </Card>
  <Card title="Back-End Management" icon="server" href="/docs/back-end-integration/index">
    Manage balances, webhooks, and transaction history from your server.
  </Card>
  <Card title="Compliance & Reporting" icon="shield-check" href="/docs/back-end-integration/endpoints/apple-compliance-events">
    Automate reporting and stay compliant with banking regulations.
  </Card>
</CardGroup>

